using namespace std;

long long t,n,a[10000],i,b[10000],n1 ;

while(t--)
{
	cin>>n ;
	memset(b,0,sizeof(b));
	for(i=0;i<n;i++){
	cin>>a[i] ;
	n1=a[i];
	b[n1]++;
	}
	sort(a,a+n);

	{
	    n1=a[i];
	if(b[n1]==1)

    cout<<a[i]<<endl ;

}
}
}

	return 0;
}
